<h1>PharmaFlow&#8482; AI Capabilities</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Intelligence Across Every Pharmacy Setting</p>
<p class="badge">Operational Intelligence</p>

<hr>

<!-- ==================== OUTPATIENT ==================== -->
<h2>1. Outpatient Pharmacy AI</h2>

<h3>Wait Time Prediction</h3>
<ul>
<li>Real-time estimates based on queue depth, prescription complexity, and robotic utilization</li>
<li>Appointment slot optimization to distribute demand evenly</li>
</ul>

<h3>Failed Pickup Prevention</h3>
<ul>
<li>No-show probability scoring per prescription</li>
<li>Proactive reminder sequences for high-risk pickups</li>
<li>Return-to-stock optimization to reduce waste</li>
</ul>

<h3>Queue &amp; Workflow Optimization</h3>
<ul>
<li>Intelligent queue prioritization based on complexity &amp; urgency</li>
<li>Multi-window balancing for minimum wait times</li>
<li>Real-time bottleneck detection and rerouting</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<!-- ==================== INPATIENT ==================== -->
<h2>2. Inpatient Pharmacy AI</h2>

<h3>Smart Order Screening</h3>
<ul>
<li>Auto-verification candidates for expedited pharmacist review</li>
<li>High-risk order flagging with patient-specific risk factors</li>
<li>Prescriber pattern analysis for compliance monitoring</li>
</ul>

<h3>Cycle Fill Optimization</h3>
<ul>
<li>Ward-level demand prediction based on patient census, admission/discharge patterns</li>
<li>Batch preparation scheduling aligned with nursing shift changes</li>
</ul>

<h3>Ward AI</h3>
<ul>
<li>Expiry risk scoring with redistribution suggestions</li>
<li>Emergency stock prediction based on patient acuity scores</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<!-- ==================== PDM NETWORK ==================== -->
<h2>3. PDM&#8482; Network AI</h2>
<p class="section-subtitle">Network-level intelligence across all PDM&#8482; branches</p>

<h3>Demand Forecasting</h3>
<p>Location-specific prediction with event-driven adjustments and new location estimation</p>

<h3>Stock Optimization</h3>
<p>Network-wide inventory balancing, FEFO enforcement, cross-branch transfer recommendations</p>

<h3>Queue Balancing</h3>
<p>Robotic utilization optimization and maintenance window planning during low-demand periods</p>

<h3>Anomaly Detection</h3>
<p>Usage pattern anomalies, equipment health monitoring, environmental tracking</p>

<h4>Key Metrics</h4>
