<!-- ==================== ENTERPRISE ==================== -->
<h2>4. Enterprise AI</h2>
<p class="section-subtitle">Cross-platform intelligence for the entire pharmacy operation</p>

<h3>Inventory &amp; Supply Chain Intelligence</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Intelligent Procurement:</b> Optimal purchase orders based on demand forecasts, stock levels, lead times, and budget</li>
<li><b>Supplier Scoring:</b> Rankings based on delivery reliability, pricing trends, and quality metrics</li>
<li><b>Expiry Prediction:</b> Identifies at-risk medications and suggests redistribution or promotion</li>
<li><b>Batch Recall Analysis:</b> Instant identification of affected stock across all locations</li>
</ul>

<h3>Operational Analytics &amp; Reporting</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Predictive KPI Alerts:</b> Alerts when metrics trend toward threshold breaches before they occur</li>
<li><b>Root Cause Analysis:</b> Correlates multiple data sources to identify performance dip causes</li>
<li><b>Natural Language Reporting:</b> AI-generated narrative reports from operational data</li>
<li><b>Conversational Analytics:</b> Query data using natural language</li>
</ul>

<h3>Compliance &amp; Regulatory AI</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Automated Compliance Monitoring:</b> Flags when configurations may need updates for regulatory changes</li>
<li><b>Audit Trail Intelligence:</b> Proactive identification of compliance gaps before external audits</li>
<li><b>HIMSS/JCI Gap Analysis:</b> Continuous evaluation against accreditation requirements</li>
</ul>

<h3>Smart Integration Engine</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Message Transformation Learning:</b> AI learns HL7/FHIR mapping patterns for new endpoints</li>
<li><b>Integration Health Monitoring:</b> Predicts interface failures from latency and error patterns</li>
<li><b>Data Quality Scoring:</b> Scores incoming data quality from HIS/ERP systems</li>
</ul>

