<!-- ==================== OSSI PARTNERSHIP ==================== -->
<h2>5. Strategic AI Partnership</h2>

<h3>PharmaFlow&#8482; &times; OSSI &mdash; Medical Data Governance&reg; (MDG&reg;)</h3>
<p class="badge">Partnership</p>

<p>FutureGate Healthcare Solutions has entered a strategic partnership with OSSI to add AI capabilities to the PharmaFlow&#8482; platform, leveraging OSSI&rsquo;s latest technologies in this domain.</p>

<p>The partnership is built on a foundation of trusted, regulated data through OSSI&rsquo;s Medical Data Governance&reg; (MDG&reg;) platform &mdash; enabling smarter, safer, and more efficient dispensing and supply chain management across outpatient and inpatient settings.</p>

