<!-- ==================== GOVERNANCE ==================== -->
<h2>6. AI Governance Framework</h2>

<p>AI optimizes operations&mdash;never bypasses governance or pharmacist oversight. All AI recommendations require human approval for clinical decisions.</p>

<h3>Core Principles</h3>

<h4>Human-in-the-Loop</h4>
<p>AI suggests &mdash; humans decide. Pharmacist oversight always maintained.</p>

<h4>Explainability</h4>
<p>Every AI decision is explainable with confidence scores and contributing factors.</p>

<h4>Auditability</h4>
<p>Complete audit trails with immutable decision logs and model version tracking.</p>

<h3>Governance Pillars</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Bias Monitoring:</b> Continuous fairness audits</li>
<li><b>Data Privacy:</b> Anonymization &amp; HIPAA compliance</li>
<li><b>Fail-Safe Design:</b> Graceful degradation &amp; manual fallback</li>
<li><b>Model Lifecycle:</b> Versioning, A/B testing, drift detection</li>
</ul>

